In [19]:
StationNumberList = measurements400['StationNumber'].tolist()
for i in StationNumberList:
    df400ID = i
    df400ID = df[df['StationNumber'] == i]
    df400ID['Time-only'] = pd.to_datetime(df400ID['Local Time'], format='%H:%M').dt.time
    concTimePlotID = i
    plt.figure()
    concTimePlotID = df400ID.plot(x='Time-only', y='Value', marker='o', linestyle='None', title= i + ' NO3N Concentration vs. Time for Stations > 400 Measurements',
                                                    figsize=(15,10)
                                                    )
    concTimePlotID.set_xlabel('Local Time')
    concTimePlotID.set_ylabel('NO3N Concentration in mg/L')
    concTimePlotID.axhline(10, color="red", linestyle="--") #reference line at  EPA Maximum Contaminant Level (MCL) of 10 mg/L
    plt.show()
